messages.message:
*In AI Hub - Build:*

*When defining a `List Extraction` field and configuring `attributes` :*
• :question-block: *Is it possible to reorder attributes during configuration without having to remove/re-add them?* 
• Additionally, the order of fields is important (in that earlier fields can not be used for later fields)
    ◦ :question-block: *Is the order of attributes within a List Extraction similar?* 
    ◦ There's no current issue inspiring the following question, just out of curiosity:
        ▪︎ :question-block: *Can attribute values even be referenced between each other?*
the answer to all of your questions is no because the order shouldn’t matter and attributes can’t reference other attributes
